      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a basic set of wheels to get you from A to B? This car is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little DIY! While it definitely shows its age and will need some mechanical attention and cosmetic TLC, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a vehicle at a very accessible price point. Grab a bargain and bring this diamond in the rough back to life!",
