      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as a project car or for parts. The engine has significant mechanical issues, including several noticeable leaks and a rough idle, while the transmission struggles to engage properly in higher gears. The exterior shows substantial wear with rust spots and faded paint, and the interior requires a complete overhaul due to heavy staining and torn upholstery. It is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed. This is an ideal candidate for someone with the mechanical expertise to perform a full restoration or who needs a donor vehicle for specific components.",
