      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone who doesn't mind a bit of character. While the engine and transmission are solid, the exterior shows some age with minor dings and clear coat fading on the roof. The interior is clean but has visible wear on the driver's seat and a few cracked trim pieces. It is currently due for a standard service and some suspension bushings may need replacement soon, but it remains a functional and honest car for the price.",
