    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This example boasts a reinforced rear subframe, a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, and a factory M-variable differential lock. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specs with zero bushing deflection, and the rod bearings have been proactively addressed. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the chassis is free of any structural fatigue or oxidative corrosion. A turnkey, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
